### Phone Data Analysis

Flipkart is a famous Indian E-Commerce website, that offers a wide range of products right from clothing to electronics to edibles to home appliances and whatnot. 


### Content
The data used in this dataset has been extracted from the Flipkart website by Web Scraping. The following attributes of the product are our key interest
⦁ Mobile Name
⦁ RAM and ROM Specification
⦁ Ratings and Reviews
⦁ Stars
⦁ List and Sales Price
